<template>
  <MainHeader v-if="!isLoginRoute" />
  <BasicHeader v-if="isLoginRoute" />
</template>

<script>
import BasicHeader from './components/BasicHeader.vue';
import MainHeader from './components/MainHeader.vue';
export default {
  name: 'App',
  components: {
    MainHeader,
    BasicHeader
  },
  computed: {
    isLoginRoute() {
      return this.$route.path === '/login';
    }
  }

}
</script>
